{"tid":683820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭支持率急瀉　上任新低","createTime":"2018-05-30T04:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T15:23:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":115,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba83b56a7c9cec76d537ea51a7b6e212033e7f5","tid":683820,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:19:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180530/20405387\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180530%2F20405387&d=bJKBWPzbAlOPooFAOkuCoG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7a8d2ca9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180530%2F20405387&h=39190a55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180530/20405387</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月30日 <br />\n<br />\n林鄭支持率急瀉　上任新低<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180530/large/30la3p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180530%2Flarge%2F30la3p5.jpg&h=8d34d76c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林鄭昨出席行會前接收請願信。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【港大民研】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥上任將近一年，表現似乎未獲市民肯定。港大最新民調顯示，市民對林鄭的評分、支持率和反對率皆去到她上任以來最差數字，連帶港府民望同告下跌，甚至對一國兩制的信心亦去到雨傘運動爆發的2014年9月以來新低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一國兩制信心跌至負數<br />\n<br />\n港大民意研究計劃於本月21日至25日調查林鄭民望，之前發生香港記者在內地被打，林鄭拒公開譴責，而市民對林鄭的評分較本月初急跌5.1分至52.7分，支持比率更大挫10個百分點至39%，反對比率增加9個百分點至44%，換言之其支持率淨值僅負5%，與月初的13%差天共地。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭民望急瀉的同時，港府亦不能倖免。市民對港府表現滿意率由37%減至30%、不滿率則由41%增至48%。與此同時，港人信任港府的比率、對目前經濟、民生、政治狀況的滿意率全線下跌，跌幅由少6個百分點至10個百分點不等，當中以民生問題的滿意率跌幅最大。<br />\n<br />\n調查結果亦顯示，港人信任中央政府的比率、對香港、內地和一國兩制前途的信心同樣下跌，各項下跌的指數中，以內地前途信心淨值和一國兩制信心淨值下跌最嚴重，前者由45%下挫至30%，後者由0%跌至負14%。<br />\n<br />\n港大民研研究經理李偉健指，林鄭民望較兩星期前顯著下跌，其評分、支持率、反對率和民望淨值全部均為上任以來最差數字。至於經濟、民生、政治三方面中，市民最不滿的仍然是政治狀況，其滿意淨值為負52%。<br />\n<br />\n而3項信心指標也顯著下跌，當中對一國兩制的信心淨值為負14%是2014年9月以來新低。<br />\n<br />\n■記者呂浩然  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n中聯辦操控80%港出版市場<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n西環集中營：髮gel特權風波　梁振英種禍根 (季陶)"},{"pid":"59e175b74b361a3eda19305419b56b53454a8cbe","tid":683820,"uid":157362,"like":72,"dislike":2,"score":70,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:21:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b2241cc75c4a304bdbbba2b4bd04f8f04b7aa7c","tid":683820,"uid":65686,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:21:35.000Z","msg":"低處未算低"},{"pid":"921f8f6f01dd97cec8a94087b88fa03f87cdc661","tid":683820,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:21:55.000Z","msg":"資源已袋"},{"pid":"2aa6c2df138893b0fc5cfd461ecd984fe1312c47","tid":683820,"uid":79563,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:22:49.000Z","msg":"低又點?<br />\n<br />\n泛民耐佢乜何?"},{"pid":"7a749f31a04c5c6730b4adc25caf1898953b0ec6","tid":683820,"uid":57023,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"一個連'你母語係乜?'都唔敢答既傀儡奴才, 仲有乜野可俾市民寄望及尊敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423384f83e05c42d2f91d24a3c6219da320dc96c","tid":683820,"uid":10757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:29:17.000Z","msg":"民望如浮雲 有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4749888e50d8f5335ce1365dc45dab357fa4d32","tid":683820,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:33:45.000Z","msg":"仲有39%噃"},{"pid":"8a4436a47a8b4a8e891259fe0a3252a7a69daa7e","tid":683820,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a1ee23fb4e28ebc79d8974893e9182fe4ab8b00","tid":683820,"uid":28831,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:38:54.000Z","msg":"跌到落3.9咪又係繼續做到任期完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1f7faef7969c40fd6a2abcef8fa38b7af2a843","tid":683820,"uid":50740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"52分已經好高"},{"pid":"2fbcc1a22030a6ff76641e5db1d8f4d7e21d68ff","tid":683820,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"奴才一隻"},{"pid":"92afaac8b273b9d3101d4eb73a47568e3f53d1d9","tid":683820,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"掛住做奴才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5caaa0d124acbe3d1edf9e1347ffa8a0a39178c","tid":683820,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"任何一隻狗民望低係正常<br />\n<br />\n何況民意如浮雲<br />\n<br />\n乜要理架"},{"pid":"7df0bbaf4e83c8866874cc412c83532d3449fcdc","tid":683820,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T05:00:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03dad0add589a5c247858106d843033473bda3b2","tid":683820,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T05:21:11.000Z","msg":"邊度會有人支持佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b981c1d2a529063470965179622891353d4a61","tid":683820,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"仲有39%人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a139774647fcf93da2da0d005d8d660c99524f78","tid":683820,"uid":126312,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T05:33:19.000Z","msg":"理得你幾分, 個個月出份糧冇少到, 做ON9野奶共出哂面. 睇你班港豬惡唔出樣, 不知幾爽."},{"pid":"1320dfc801ec656b2eef3e919fd9eae9d85a64ce","tid":683820,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a749f31a04c5c6730b4adc25caf1898953b0ec6","tid":683820,"uid":57023,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"cite